  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  fibrous dysplasia of bone

          -  previously treated with IV bisphosphonates

          -  persistent bone pain and increased bone remodeling

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic renal failure

          -  serious infectious diseases

          -  liver enzymes abnormality

          -  pregnancy

          -  dyslipidemia
      </textblock>
